  <div class="paragraph">
    <p> Topics include basic algebra, linear equations, quadratic equations, functions and graphs,
      inequalities, logarithms and exponential functions, mathematics of finance, linear programming, matrices, systems 
      of linear equations, and applications to management, economics, and business.
       
    </p>
